speed wobbles
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number:
Definition:unsteadiness or uncertainty caused by rapid progress or change (especially political or economic change)
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Domain:[none]
Region:[none]
See:
Pronunciation:
Notes: first used by Prime Minister Geoffrey Palmer of the Labour government's reforms in the 1980s
